<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=5 f=1 -->
39
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
 As suggested in the comments, these changes should substantially reduce the number of persons for whom such Schedules
must be prepared and filed under the reproposed rule. 
