would minimize the amount of communication among members of an investment complex that would be necessary to complete
Form 13H. Moreover, these changes to the proposed rule would conform with the various rules and regulations that require
financial institutions of all types to identify the beneficial owners of accounts, confirm trades, and maintain
possession and control of customer funds and securities. 
