<!-- PJG ITAG l=83 g=1 f=1 -->
D. Trade Reporting Requirements of Brokers and Dealers 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
Section 13(h)(2) of the Exchange Act specifically authorizes the Commission to require registered broker-dealers
to report transactions that equal or exceed the reporting activity level effected by or through such broker-dealer
for persons who they know are large traders, or any persons who they have reason to know are large traders on the basis
of transactions effected by or through such broker-dealers.
