<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
The reporting activity level contained in paragraph (e)(2)(i) of the reproposed rule would increase the thresholds
contained in the proposed rule from 1,000 to 2,000 shares, and from a fair market value of $40,000 to $100,000. The reproposed
