<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
After carefully weighing costs and benefits, the Commission has decided to repropose the Division's alternative
for reducing the burdens of the execution time reporting requirements. The reproposed reporting requirements are
found in new paragraphs (e) (3) and (4). 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
Paragraph (e)(3) of the reproposed rule would provide that with respect to system orders, all transaction information
