prior to trade comparison and would consider pertinent market conditions as well as the capabilities of the industry's
trade processing facilities.
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=5 f=1 -->
66
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
 Moreover, under the reproposed rule, the Commission may require the transmission of transaction reports after final
settlement because of the inclusion of cancellations and corrections within the definition of a transaction.
