and
<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=21 g=1 f=1 -->
 (2) an aggregate calendar year total of 2,000,000 shares or fair market value of $30,000,000. Any inactive large trader
that subsequently effects transactions that again reach the identifying activity level must make an initial filing
within 10 business days after it effects the ``re-identifying transactions.'' 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

