(g) The agency will, to the maximum extent possible consistent with the legal obligations of the agency, use the consensus
of the committee with respect to the proposed rules as the basis for the rules proposed by the agency for notice and comment.
Negotiated Rulemaking Act Sec. 3, 5 U.S.C. 583(a). 
