<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
The Secretary also proposes to make clear that an 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
institution is responsible for repayment of any funds owed by its 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
servicer until those funds are repaid by the servicer. The 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
Secretary considers this provision necessary because an 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
institution is always responsible for the actions of its agents. 
