<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
Indicators of questionable past performance would be_ 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
(1) A limitation, suspension, or termination action by the 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
Secretary against the servicer within the preceding five 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->
years; 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

